Terrorsaur:



Terrosaur followed the signatures of the other Predacons to the base, 
and landed inside with Golden Eye in his arms. He walked through the 
hallways until he reached the CR room. He placed Golden Eye in one of 
the tanks, and went entered one himself to ease his wings.
